  "Description": "The StartNostrListener goal initializes a listener for new messages based on the configuration specified in the ../nostr.config file. It reads the npub from the config file to avoid an ask loop and sets up a listener for messages directed to the target specified in the configuration. When a new message is received, it triggers the OnNostrMessage goal.",
